{"id": 1026, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在生活中遭遇过哪些“小确讨嫌”的事情？", "description": "那些讨厌程度介于“fine”和“滚你丫的！”之间的讨嫌行为，为此发脾气显得我戾气重，但忍你我真的难受。（题图来自：Amelie Fontaine）", "record_count": 10680, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181401p5ZBiskcLAYMXqyz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-04T01:00:26Z", "options": [{"id": 84736, "content": "故意讨好", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628522}, {"id": 84992, "content": "拿贪便宜当聪明", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590799}, {"id": 84737, "content": "逛服装店把衣服弄的乱七八糟", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584951}, {"id": 84993, "content": "不刷牙的家伙！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126700}, {"id": 85249, "content": "让我晚上不准打蚊子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635583}, {"id": 84738, "content": "工作需要电话沟通，明明电话就在手边却故意不接。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634397}, {"id": 84994, "content": "擅自用别人的水杯喝水", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635087}, {"id": 85506, "content": "书店站着翻书时，有人过来靠得很近、超过心理安全距离也开始翻书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110005}, {"id": 84739, "content": "大概是 在一起说话 突然飙出了口水 正对着我", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634400}, {"id": 84996, "content": "别人睡觉时候讲话", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612568}, {"id": 85764, "content": "大家说的这些都是我认为小却讨厌的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600679}, {"id": 88068, "content": "无休止的修改", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643762}, {"id": 84741, "content": "扣完鼻子，动我手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494121}, {"id": 85765, "content": "大家说的这些大部分都是我认为小却讨厌的≥﹏≤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600679}, {"id": 84742, "content": "每次看视频看得正爽的时候，手机突然跳出一个框：您的手机还剩20%的电量…声音还巨大", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634260}, {"id": 84998, "content": "拿手机给别人看图片TA却滑动屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613710}, {"id": 85254, "content": "拿别人的缺陷开玩笑！我们很熟嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 625851}, {"id": 88838, "content": "无意间翻白眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219928}, {"id": 84999, "content": "乱扔垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617310}, {"id": 85255, "content": "在别人家乱翻别人的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634996}, {"id": 85511, "content": "挡路的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636091}, {"id": 86023, "content": "午睡时候，不懂得安静?。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637618}, {"id": 84744, "content": "密闭空间抽烟全然不顾别人的感受", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631192}, {"id": 85000, "content": "貌似说的这么多都是“滚你丫的”范围内的", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635125}, {"id": 85256, "content": "人多的时候打电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635593}, {"id": 85512, "content": "无意打断我说话、但是次数有点多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469959}, {"id": 85768, "content": "一天内不同时间段发给她两次消息，不回。却看到她发朋友圈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628711}, {"id": 84745, "content": "随意拿不熟的人的东西用，用完也不还回来(╯￣Д￣)╯", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634426}, {"id": 85001, "content": "在寝室说话很大声", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635129}, {"id": 85257, "content": "微信清人", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635593}, {"id": 86281, "content": "1.工作经常各种理由请假把事丢给别人做。2.自己不做怪别人做太多显得自己无能。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533858}, {"id": 84746, "content": "气氛活泼的谈话中非要直截了当指出你的意图。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572702}, {"id": 86282, "content": "人都起来了，闹钟还不关，隔一会响一会", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632917}, {"id": 84747, "content": "吃饭吧唧嘴，喝水吸溜吸溜的", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 206007}, {"id": 85003, "content": "两个月不洗澡的室友……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635134}, {"id": 85771, "content": "求转帮赞 从来没在微信上聊过一开口就是求帮忙 您哪位啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508873}, {"id": 85004, "content": "口臭还拉着你一直说话 还凑得格外近！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498475}, {"id": 85516, "content": "洗脸的时候醒鼻涕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635674}, {"id": 85261, "content": "在我附近小声聊天，虽然听不到说什么但是能听见嘀嘀咕咕的声音?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598775}, {"id": 85773, "content": "默认个人的物品就是全宿舍的共同财产 随便用", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508873}, {"id": 85774, "content": "啰嗦，说话没重点（就是我）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624574}, {"id": 84751, "content": "仗着跟我关系好就随便讲话", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548295}, {"id": 85007, "content": "手贱闲的慌扣人家东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105336}, {"id": 85519, "content": "死直男", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636105}, {"id": 84752, "content": "不经我允许乱动我东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246101}, {"id": 85008, "content": "图书馆里说悄悄话", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635144}, {"id": 85520, "content": "无论你在干什么都要过来问一句：你干嘛呢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631795}, {"id": 84753, "content": "进了别人的房间不随手关门", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585687}, {"id": 85009, "content": "给别人看手机里照片的时候她来回滑！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635143}, {"id": 85521, "content": "忘记关灯出寝室", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636103}]}